headline: Can Agilent Technologies' (A) Genomic Automation Push Reinforce Its Edge in a Competitive Diagnostics Market?
summary: Agilent Technologies recently participated in the Industrial Transformation ASIA-PACIFIC 2025 conference in Singapore, highlighting its role in advancing automated genetic sequencing and diagnostics through collaborations, including new genomic workflow protocols announced by SPT Labtech in partnership with Agilent. This wave of innovation comes as Agilent strengthens its leadership across genetic testing and the microfluidics market, both of which are seeing increased interest due to...
